{"tid":2214139,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【離晒譜】尼馬竟辱罵「中國人是狗屎」，有機會停賽10場！","createTime":"2020-09-23T04:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T05:46:00.000Z","uid":5680,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0bfa19492800dd2ccf3a9fcaf48491840286c50c","tid":2214139,"uid":5680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"較早前法甲一場大戰，巴黎聖日耳門與馬賽最終以多人被逐收場，其中PSG核心尼馬便是其中收下紅牌嘅球員之一。而近日，尼馬疑似被證實說出侮辱之句，因此有機會被追加停賽場數。<br />\n<br />\n據指，尼馬與比賽期間曾向馬賽日本球員酒井宏樹說出「辱華」字句「Chino de mierda」（可翻譯為「中國人是狗屎」），相信係因為尼馬分唔清亞洲人，將日本人同中國人搞亂，呢一點酒井宏樹應該都幾無奈，大佬人地日本人你就話佢係中國人，比我都唔高興啦。<br />\nCredit: Getty Images<br />\n不過尼馬賽後亦指對手守將艾華路干沙利斯涉嫌種族歧視，但尼馬目前已經因為偷襲對手後腦，而已被停賽2場，而其他指控則仍在調查中，如果證實尼馬曾說出侮辱字句，佢將有機會被重罰停賽10場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=sports&amp;aid=24808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fmobile%2Farticle%2Farticle.php%3Fcat%3Dsports%26aid%3D24808&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9tTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=d85207ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=sports&amp;aid=24808</a>"},{"pid":"cc878348fd4dadcbda5ff7786792eadde05fbda2","tid":2214139,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"侮辱狗"},{"pid":"c226be31aa00f5763fe66c476511970386db145e","tid":2214139,"uid":8308,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"好心痛 點解要咁樣侮辱狗屎"},{"pid":"2b2c1c752a033f7f48840a481e050201c23d1363","tid":2214139,"uid":13013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"日本仔慘"},{"pid":"b860c9d1728ac20fed3bd6cfa21206abc813707e","tid":2214139,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c226be31aa00f5763fe66c476511970386db145e","tid":2214139,"uid":8308,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"好心痛 點解要咁樣侮辱狗屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T04